So thank you very, very much.

00:34:10.350 --> 00:34:12.750
If you would like to
have your books signed,

00:34:12.750 --> 00:34:15.830
then Xiaolu will
be here for you.

00:34:15.830 --> 00:34:18.220
So please give a round
of applause for Xiaolu.

